GETTING THE LATEST CODE:

  kohana:
    - v2.2 from http://kohanaphp.com/download (no languages, only auth plugin)

  kohanamodules:
    - svn export http://kohanamodules.googlecode.com/svn/tags/2.2/forge

  kohana-mptt:
    - cd mptt/libraries && svn export http://kohana-mptt.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/MPTT.php


WHERE EVERYTHING GOES IN GALLERY3.
  Note: This is how the files got installed initially, this is NOT how you
  update them!

  $ cd gallery3
  $ svn cp vendor/kohana/system trunk/kohana
  $ svn cp "vendor/kohana/Kohana License.html" trunk/kohana/KohanaLicense.html
  $ svn cp vendor/kohanamodules/forge trunk/modules
  $ svn cp vendor/kohana-mptt/mptt trunk/modules



